# Views/Components Directory
# 
# This directory should contain reusable UI components:
# - PrimaryButton.swift (styled button component)
# - LoadingView.swift (loading indicator)
# - ErrorView.swift (error display component)
# - EmptyStateView.swift (empty list/data view)
# - TextFieldView.swift (custom text input)
# - CardView.swift (card container component)
# - BadgeView.swift (notification badges)
# - AvatarView.swift (user avatar display)
# - ToastView.swift (toast notifications)
# 
# Components should be:
# - Highly reusable across different screens
# - Configurable through parameters
# - Focused on presentation only (no business logic)